criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Sign the informed consent form voluntarily;

          2. Experimental group: Patients with pancreatic ductal adenocarcinoma found by
             preoperative imaging and after surgical resection;

          3. Control group: healthy people of similar age without any benign or malignant diseases;

        Exclusion Criteria:

        1. Case group:

          1. Use neoadjuvant chemotherapy before surgery;

          2. Consider pancreatic MT before surgery, and postoperative pathology for patients with
             non-pancreatic ductal adenocarcinoma;

          3. Second surgery; 2. Control group:

        1) The tumor index detection is abnormal, and it is still abnormal after re-examination.
